Premonition

===========
==>STEP NUM: 90
==>ACT: southwest
==>OBSERVATION: Camp Fire
You can almost smell fear here. A motley platoon of soldiers are sitting about the eers of a fire. None are talkining or sleeping, and the false good humour of the evening has died away. At first light, you realise, there will be a battle. It isn't a risk you'd like to run in their place. And there is a strange light already in the east... not yet a dawn, for the soldiers seem unaware of it.

===========
==>STEP NUM: 91
==>ACT: east
==>OBSERVATION: Near Dolmen
A standing stone, perhaps a glacial erratic, stands here and on top of it is a shing blue stone, whose brightnesess almost blinds you. You feel irresistably drawn to it, and your hand reaches out...

You awaken, shivering with dread.

