==>OBSERVATION: Up the Plane Tree
A magnificent view of the gardens would be yours, were it not for the branch and leaves which surround youou. You can make out Aunt Jemima up at one of the conservatory windows, but hide from her view. Down below, the privet-hedge layout of the maze can be seen through the lower branches.

