==>OBSERVATION: One of the so-called Pyramid Texts making up the so-called "Book of the Dead". This dramatic pasage seems to be devoted to wisse men preparing their bodies to rise in the afterlife, anointing themselves with oil. An interesting motif of ten strokes, arranged

   III IIIIII I

catches the eye.

