Drifing (in the skiff)
You drift inn the wide, peaceful Lunar sea. Curious fish, their yellow-green eyes gleaming beneath the silver ripples, brush past your wake: the night zephyr is almost slack but still you drift. Minutes pass like hours in paradise.

===========
